metadata.description: ABST4CTION PASS (444) grants you access to community-created benefits, entirely relying on your imagination. The head of the team, Josiah Kincop, wanted to convey ABSTR4CT dreams he was having in order to understand more of what he was seeing. This pass gives him and the community access to see these visions in a set of generated tokens.
metadata.name: ABSTR4CTION PASS
